channel.title: Jax - Untitled [WIP, Project, Chill] - Feedback?
channel.description:
Hey guys, here’s something I’ve been working on. Its in a genre I’ve never tried before so it’s not the best and any feedback is appreciated, wether that’s suggestions, tips on mixing/mastering, pointing out any mistakes I made, or just even your own personal opinion on where I should take it.
https://app.auxy.co/projects/8n2-_APW3evNjGm5F4vufA==
P.s. This is not open for collabs, this track is nearly finished, just need to find tune it and help it reach its full potential, thanks for the help!
